teacheasy.xml

Enum XMLAttribute

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<XMLAttribute>
      • teacheasy.xml.XMLAttribute
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<XMLAttribute>

    public enum XMLAttribute
extends java.lang.Enum<XMLAttribute>
    This enumerated type contains an entry for any attribute the parser anticipates finding within an xml file. This allows for the 'string switching' method seen in the XMLParser class.
    Version:
    1.0 13 Feb 2015
    Author:
    Alistair Jewers
